{
  "stem": "9995.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I said, they not going to find anything from me, even if I have to drop dead to do it eating this, which I ate.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But at any rate, they took us, and they gave each one of us 25.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were about to kill us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the guy for whom we work, his name was Bulb.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He came in, and he said, release my people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So just before they were about to shoot the whole place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Of course they-- once in a while, they were looking what you are bringing into camp, and especially if you are bringing some food, then they were killing you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he came in and saw in the last second, they took us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "However, what I have seen, at that day, I will also never forget.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a place where only 40 people work. 39 men and 1 woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was absolutely gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was married to the engineer who was in charge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They called it, SS Bonarka, because the place in Cracow where they worked, they were doing some-- I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But for the Germans, something, building whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they also brought a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were just before us coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they took them on the little hill where they were killing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We're supposed to be killed next.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians were killing those people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And after they shot all of them, they shot the girl, but such a way that she was not dead yet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then they raped her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And when I saw it, I said, oh my God, why don't I have-- my mother asked me to carry poison with me, and I didn't.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because I said, that's what they're going to do also to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
